          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1583491462963-x1000.jpg",
            "width": 1000
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-5-1583491462963-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the steaks are done, add them to a plate and set aside to rest</p><p>Add the<strong> chopped cherry tomatoes </strong>and<strong> remaining whole cherry tomatoes </strong>to the pan along with the <strong>rosemary leaves </strong>and <strong>crushed garlic </strong>and cook for 1-2 min or until the tomatoes have started to soften</p><p>Once softened, add 50ml <span class=\"text-danger\">[50ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong> and a large knob of <strong>butter</strong> and mix it all together  – this is your <strong>pan sauce</strong></p>",
      "order": 6,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1583491466337-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1583491466337-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1583491466337-x700.jpg",
