          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1583491466337-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the polenta has thickened, add the <strong>clotted cream</strong> and <strong>grated Italian hard cheese</strong> and give it a really good mix up, removing any lumps – this is your <strong>cheesy polenta</strong></p><p>Finely slice the <strong>rested</strong> <strong>steaks</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1583491469925-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1583491469925-x400.jpg",
            "width": 400
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1583491469925-x700.jpg",
