            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>cheesy polenta</strong> in bowls and top with the <strong>sliced steak</strong></p><p>Pour over the <strong>pan sauce</strong> and <strong>cherry tomatoes</strong> and top with a grind of <strong>black pepper</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
